---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Seth Boss Guide - Hollow Knight: Silksong"
  description="Complete strategy guide for defeating Seth in Hollow Knight: Silksong. Learn attack patterns, recommended builds, and winning strategies."
  keywords="seth boss guide, silksong seth strategy, seth boss fight, hollow knight silksong seth"
>
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
          <img src="/images/bosses/seth_3.avif" alt="Seth Boss" class="w-48 h-48 rounded-lg shadow-2xl" />
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-6">
          <span class="gradient-text">Seth Boss Guide</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Defeat the mysterious Seth with proven strategies and tactics
        </p>

        <!-- Tribute Section -->
        <div class="bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg p-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
            <img src="/images/bosses/seth_5.webp" alt="Seth Goldman Concept Art" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-lg mr-4" />
            <div class="text-left">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-400">Community Tribute</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Original concept art by Seth Goldman</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
            This boss was inspired by community artwork and named in tribute to a beloved community member.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Boss Stats -->
        <div class="bg-silksong-dark/50 rounded-lg p-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-400">High</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Difficulty</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-400">Main Boss</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Type</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-400">Mid Game</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Timing</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">Story</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Progression</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Strategy -->
      <div class="bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/30 rounded-lg p-6 mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-400">⚡ Quick Strategy Summary</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-white">Key Tactics:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
              <li>• Watch for ground shockwave telegraphs</li>
              <li>• Use aerial attacks when possible</li>
              <li>• Time your dodges carefully</li>
              <li>• Focus on hit-and-run tactics</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-white">Phase 2 Warning:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
              <li>• Powerful shockwave attacks</li>
              <li>• Increased movement speed</li>
              <li>• New attack patterns emerge</li>
              <li>• Environment becomes hazardous</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 2 Shockwave Guide -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Phase 2: Shockwave Strategy</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

          <div class="bg-silksong-dark rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
              <img src="/images/bosses/seth_13.avif" alt="Seth Phase 2 Shockwave" class="w-full max-w-sm rounded-lg" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-orange-400">Shockwave Attack Pattern</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
              In Phase 2, Seth gains powerful ground-based shockwave attacks that can cover significant portions of the arena. These are telegraphed but require precise timing to avoid.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-orange-500/10 rounded p-4">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-orange-300 mb-2">Counter Strategy:</h4>
              <ul class="text-gray-300 text-sm space-y-1">
                <li>• Jump or dash just as the shockwave is released</li>
                <li>• Use walls for extended air time</li>
                <li>• Position yourself at arena edges when possible</li>
                <li>• Time your attacks between shockwave cycles</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-silksong-dark rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-400">Recommended Tools</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">

              <div class="flex items-center bg-blue-500/10 rounded p-3">
                <img src="/images/bosses/seth_7.avif" alt="Pale Nails" class="w-12 h-12 rounded mr-3" />
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-400">Pale Nails</h4>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Enhanced damage output</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-center bg-red-500/10 rounded p-3">
                <img src="/images/bosses/seth_8.avif" alt="Reaper Crest" class="w-12 h-12 rounded mr-3" />
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-400">Reaper Crest</h4>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Defensive tool slots</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-center bg-yellow-500/10 rounded p-3">
                <img src="/images/bosses/seth_9.avif" alt="Straight Pin" class="w-12 h-12 rounded mr-3" />
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-yellow-400">Straight Pin</h4>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Ranged attack option</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-center bg-green-500/10 rounded p-3">
                <img src="/images/bosses/seth_10.avif" alt="Tacks" class="w-12 h-12 rounded mr-3" />
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-400">Tacks</h4>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Area denial tool</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-center bg-purple-500/10 rounded p-3">
                <img src="/images/bosses/seth_11.avif" alt="Warding Bell" class="w-12 h-12 rounded mr-3" />
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-purple-400">Warding Bell</h4>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Defensive utility</p>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Attack Patterns -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Complete Attack Pattern Guide</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">

          <!-- Phase 1 Attacks -->
          <div class="bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/30 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400">Phase 1 Attacks (100% - 50% HP)</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-white">Basic Melee Combo</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-2">
                  Seth performs a series of physical attacks with moderate recovery time.
                </p>
                <div class="bg-green-500/20 rounded p-2">
                  <p class="text-green-300 text-xs">
                    <strong>Counter:</strong> Dash away during combo, attack during recovery
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-white">Positioning Dash</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-2">
                  Quick movement across the arena to close distance or reposition.
                </p>
                <div class="bg-green-500/20 rounded p-2">
                  <p class="text-green-300 text-xs">
                    <strong>Counter:</strong> Use his movement to get behind him for attacks
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Phase 2 Attacks -->
          <div class="bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/30 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-orange-400">Phase 2 Attacks (50% - 0% HP)</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-white">Ground Shockwave</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-2">
                  Powerful ground-based attack that travels across the arena floor.
                </p>
                <div class="bg-orange-500/20 rounded p-2">
                  <p class="text-orange-300 text-xs">
                    <strong>Counter:</strong> Jump or use walls to stay airborne
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-white">Enhanced Combos</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-2">
                  Faster, more aggressive versions of Phase 1 attacks.
                </p>
                <div class="bg-orange-500/20 rounded p-2">
                  <p class="text-orange-300 text-xs">
                    <strong>Counter:</strong> More careful timing required, use ranged attacks
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Arena Strategy -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Arena Strategy & Positioning</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

          <div class="bg-silksong-dark rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-400">🏟️ Arena Layout</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-blue-400 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Medium-sized horizontal arena with wall-clinging opportunities</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-blue-400 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Ground-level platform with raised edges for escaping shockwaves</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-blue-400 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Multiple levels allow for vertical positioning strategies</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-blue-400 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Wall surfaces are climbable for extended air time</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-silksong-dark rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-yellow-400">🎯 Positioning Tips</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-yellow-400 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Stay near walls in Phase 2 for quick vertical escapes</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-yellow-400 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Use the center area for Phase 1 to maximize movement options</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-yellow-400 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Maintain distance when Seth is preparing shockwave attacks</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-yellow-400 mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Learn safe spots where shockwaves have reduced reach</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Difficulty Variations -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Difficulty & Build Recommendations</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

          <!-- Normal Mode -->
          <div class="bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/30 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400">🟢 Normal Mode</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">Recommended Level:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs">Mid-game progression</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">Key Tools:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs">Pale Nails, Basic defensive tools</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">Strategy:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs">Patient, methodical approach</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Hard Mode -->
          <div class="bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/30 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-orange-400">🟡 Steel Soul</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">Recommended Level:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs">Well-equipped late mid-game</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">Key Tools:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs">Full defensive suite, Reaper Crest</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">Strategy:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs">Extreme caution, perfect timing</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Speedrun -->
          <div class="bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/30 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-purple-400">🟣 Speedrun</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">Recommended Level:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs">Minimum viable equipment</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">Key Tools:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs">Damage-focused, minimal defense</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">Strategy:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs">Aggressive, risk/reward optimization</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Rewards Section -->
      <div class="bg-silksong-dark/50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-silksong-gold">Victory Rewards</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-white">Story Progression:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-300 text-sm">
              <li>• Main quest advancement</li>
              <li>• New dialogue options</li>
              <li>• Area access unlocked</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-white">Material Rewards:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-300 text-sm">
              <li>• Experience for achievement hunters</li>
              <li>• Possible tool or crest access</li>
              <li>• Progression milestone</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigation -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between gap-4">
        <a href="/guides/bosses" class="btn-secondary text-center">
          ← All Boss Guides
        </a>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <a href="/guides/bosses/lace" class="btn-secondary text-center">
            Lace Guide →
          </a>
          <a href="/checklist" class="btn-primary text-center">
            Track Progress
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B5A9F 0%, #9B59B6 50%, #BF75E6 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
</style>